By":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:13:11.000Z","msg":"雖然預左犯民會出黎騎劫<br />\n但咁點 聽日個遊行係香港人 唔係政黨架<br />\n大家唔散就得！"},{"pid":"9de8fccd21551fb7943ea8e06207983177eaed91","tid":1192000,"uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:14:52.000Z","msg":"泛民屌完人 之後話唔好互屌？"},{"pid":"57ded1895d4ad8c65764ce589a4aa774d2e25561","tid":1192000,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:16:52.000Z","msg":"劉小麗嗌捉鬼在先<br />\n打算反擊就係五毛"},{"pid":"ba9cf0b72c16c7c9c5a60b03468234a9b2e83712","tid":1192000,"uid":68302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"57ded1895d4ad8c65764ce589a4aa774d2e25561","tid":1192000,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:16:52.000Z","msg":"劉小麗嗌捉鬼在先<br />\n打算反擊就係五毛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:19:57.000Z","msg":"佢屎忽一早開哂花<br />\n等於你唔會開post話柒婆好柒<br />\n只係浪費時間"},{"pid":"5ae193aad1198febf54ed6bb0d46f63bbe6bfe27","tid":1192000,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ba9cf0b72c16c7c9c5a60b03468234a9b2e83712","tid":1192000,"uid":68302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"57ded1895d4ad8c65764ce589a4aa774d2e25561","tid":1192000,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:16:52.000Z","msg":"劉小麗嗌捉鬼在先<br />\n打算反擊就係五毛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:19:57.000Z","msg":"佢屎忽一早開哂花<br />\n等於你唔會開post話柒婆好柒<br />\n只係浪費時間"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:21:10.000Z","msg":"你幻想佢無政治能量啫"},{"pid":"ac3549ab4a404171dd46a156b9ceb11633174a3b","tid":1192000,"uid":68302,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ae193aad1198febf54ed6bb0d46f63bbe6bfe27","tid":1192000,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ba9cf0b72c16c7c9c5a60b03468234a9b2e83712","tid":1192000,"uid":68302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"57ded1895d4ad8c65764ce589a4aa774d2e25561","tid":1192000,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:16:52.000Z",