他同路人所做出嘅行為，至於唔同門派之間嘅舊仇恨，宜家大敵當前兵臨城下，都唔好互踩住（eg黃毓民、陳雲甚至熱狗之流，雖然我都覺得熱狗好賤格，但只要冇人彩佢無視佢就可以，冇必要鬧戰）否則三毛好易利用呢點製造缺口挑撥「土本vs泛民」嘅關係，造成反共力量嘅內亂。呢條守則任何反共力量（包括泛民&amp;本土）都應該要守<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6月9號！大家一齊上街！"},{"pid":"dc41c326489b034e64ff2915e725024807a0b6f7","tid":1192000,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:36:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef9083b3cecf42dbde038a6e64c7ee6c540f231","tid":1192000,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:36:11.000Z","msg":"泛民一直想消滅激進勢力<br />\n根本唔可能係同路人<br />\n泛民同激進派既關係就係共產黨同國民黨既關係"},{"pid":"87b28ab211e9cac703bd89596287be5e25b42895","tid":1192000,"uid":88123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:37:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"93b998bbe509cee19cc4074dbb55045303cc2751","tid":1192000,"uid":68302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:09:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66eea639555f79120770105fd454804a43c7da70","tid":1192000,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:11:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}